title: Counter-Strike 1.6 Soldier
description:
Counter-Strike 1.6 Soldier - Be the best player in the Counter-Strike world !
Join with other players of Cs 1.6 Game !
There are over 2 milions of players from world who play this game !
This client si a revEmulator of the original game , which is 10$ on Steam Market Store and you can play as a pro player !

How to run this game ? Just download , follow the installer instructions and play !
If there appear some problems , please leave me a comment here !

Some modifications in this versio : 
 - New GUI Menu
 - New Background GUI Menu
 - New 'Find Servers' style
 - New 'Options' style
 - New 'In Game' style
 - revEmulator to play on all CS 1.6 servers
 - Anti-Ban guard
 - A list of servers updated weekly
 - Clean Game
 - Auto join on game startup , it's more usefull for the players who wants to play a fastest CS 1.6 match

SnapShot of the GUI Menu : http://imgur.com/a/l69Hk
